I was born in Pakistan,

00:00:27.520 --> 00:00:30.560
I was born in Pakistan,

00:00:34.280 --> 00:00:38.020
near Faisalabad, district Faisalabad.

00:00:40.760 --> 00:00:43.560
What was it like growing up there?

