It was very nice.

00:00:48.920 --> 00:00:50.840
We had a small family.

00:00:54.060 --> 00:00:58.280
My father was in England.

00:00:59.920 --> 00:01:03.500
He was in the army first and then he came to England to work.

00:01:04.500 --> 00:01:12.380
